From 467d60561bc8ea186dd25846ba68ffda77243cae Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yonggang Luo <luoyonggang@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 12 Jan 2026 04:59:56 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 21/21] fixes compile with c99 with cygwin gcc 15.2

---
 exp_clib.c     | 10 ++++++----
 exp_command.h  |  6 +++---
 exp_main_sub.c |  6 +++---
